They stipulate that any "organizer of the dissemination of information on the Internet, providing the possibility of exchanging electronic messages," is obliged to identify users on the basis of information contained in the databases of telecom operators, having previously concluded agreements with them.
And also "immediately block messages or publications that contain information disseminated in violation of the requirements of Russian law."
Otherwise, operators have the right to restrict access to the service by decision of Roskomnadzor.
