Notices on the transport tax will cease to be sent by mail - site Driving www.zr.ru
The Tax Inspectorate changed the order of dispatch of notices on property taxes.
All Russian car owners are accustomed to the scheme that has not changed for years: in the summer and in the autumn they receive by mail receipts for payment of the transport tax for the previous year.
However, this year many of them will not wait.
The fact is that the tax inspection changed the order of notification of citizens without any noise.
Those who are registered in the "Personal account of the taxpayer" on the official website of the agency nalog.ru, notices will come in electronic form.
The inspection automatically found such Russians online users and deleted them from the standard, "paper" mailing.
The innovation will affect all owners of vehicles and real estate.
All the rest will still receive the usual letters.
However, the owners of the account on the site have the opportunity to return to the old scheme.
To do this, they will have to visit the tax office in August and write a statement.
On the one hand, the new order is more modern and more convenient.
The notice will appear in the "personal cabinet" immediately after the compilation, whereas the letter will go for several days and may be completely lost.
In addition, the number of users of the Internet service tax inspection exceeded 18 million people, which will allow the department to seriously save on the mailing list.
On the other hand, the modest news on the inspection site is clearly not enough to inform citizens about the changed order.
Some could register in the "private office" to receive a one-time service and have long forgotten about it.
These people will not wait for notices by mail and, without knowing it, fall into the category of defaulters with all the ensuing consequences.
Access to the "Personal account of the taxpayer" is carried out in three ways: through the account of the portal gosuslugi.ru, using an electronic signature or entering the login and password specified in the registration card.
The latter can be obtained personally in any branch of the tax inspection (regardless of the place of registration).
We remind you that this year the transport tax must be paid before December 1.
The notification mailing began in July.
